#: core/class-wcfm-admin.php:119
msgid "<p>WooCommerce Frontend Manage - Ultimate is there to fill up all those for you. Live Chat, Store Invoice, Support Ticket, Shipment Tracking, Direct Messaging, Followers, Badges, Verificaton, Product Importer, Bulk Edit and many more, almost a never ending features list for you.</p>"
msgstr ""

#: core/class-wcfm-admin.php:167
msgid "<p>A simple membership plugin for offering FREE AND PREMIUM SUBSCRIPTION for your multi-vendor marketplace. You may set up unlimited membership levels (example: free, silver, gold etc) with different pricing plan, capabilities and commission. Also you will have Pay for Product option.</p>"
msgstr ""

